Achievements.Name: First Glory
Achievements.Description: Awarded for your first win.

Achievements.Name: Winning Streak
Achievements.Description: Awarded for winning 10 consecutive matches.

Achievements.Name: Come From Behind
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you come from behind and win.

Achievements.Name: Last-minute Win
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you score the winning goal in extra time.

Achievements.Name: World Tour
Achievements.Description: Awarded for playing at all the stadiums.

Achievements.Name: Gentleman
Achievements.Description: Awarded for an average foul rate of less than 1 per match in your 10 most recent matches.

Achievements.Name: Possession Play
Achievements.Description: Awarded for achieving a possession rate of 60% or higher in your 10 most recent matches.

Achievements.Name: Hat-trick Hero
Achievements.Description: Awarded for scoring 5 hat-tricks.

Achievements.Name: Ace Striker
Achievements.Description: Awarded for playing 20 matches, scoring in recent 5, averaging 2 goals per match.

Achievements.Name: FK specialist
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you score 5 direct free-kicks.

Achievements.Name: Long Ranger
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you score from 35m or more.

Achievements.Name: League Title
Achievements.Description: A title awarded for winning one of the top leagues in [Master League]

Achievements.Name: European Elite 16
Achievements.Description: A title awarded for making the Knockout Stage of the UEFA Champions League in [Master League] .

Achievements.Name: Conquered Europe
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you win the Master League UEFA Champions League.

Achievements.Name: World Champions
Achievements.Description: Awarded for winning the Konami Cup in Master League.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Season
Achievements.Description: Awarded for an undefeated season in Master League winning League, Cup and UEFA Champions League.

Achievements.Name: No.1 Club
Achievements.Description: Awarded for topping the Club Ranking in Master League.

Achievements.Name: European Footballer of the Year
Achievements.Description: Awarded if a member of your team wins the European Footballer of the Year in Master League.

Achievements.Name: 10 years of Service
Achievements.Description: A title to honour 10 years of service in Master League.

Achievements.Name: Pro Debut
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you make your Become a Legend pro debut.

Achievements.Name: International Cup Debut
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you play in the Become a Legend International Cup.

Achievements.Name: International Cup MVP
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you receive the Become a Legend International Cup Player of the Tournament.

Achievements.Name: Wanderer
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you have played for 10 clubs in total in 4 countries in Become a Legend.

Achievements.Name: The Super Hero
Achievements.Description: Won both World Footballer of the Year and European Footballer of the Year titles in Become a Legend.

Achievements.Name: Winning Streak(Online)
Achievements.Description: Awarded when you have 5 successive Ranked match wins in the Online.

Achievements.Name: High Win Ratio(Online)
Achievements.Description: Awarded when you achieve a win ratio of above 75% in Last 20 results of Online.

Achievements.Name: Made the Knockout Stage
Achievements.Description: A title awarded for making the Knockout Stage of the UEFA Champions League.

Achievements.Name: European Champions
Achievements.Description: A title awarded when you win the UEFA Champions League.
